In the following non-compliant example, the implementation supports 6 signi ﬁ cant case-insensitive
characters in external identi ﬁ ers. The identi ﬁ ers in the two translation units are di ﬀ erent but are not
distinct in their signi ﬁ cant characters.
/* file1.c */
